articles.title: Climate activist Greta Thunberg detained by police in London - Reuters UK
articles.description: Climate activist Greta Thunberg was detained by police in London on Tuesday, a Reuters witness reported, after she and others protested outside an oil and gas conference, preventing some delegates from attending.
